    "state_reason": "completed",
    "title": "Race condition in CScheduler::serviceQueue",
    "body": "`CScheduler::serviceQueue` has the following code:\n\n```\n+            lock.unlock();\n+            f();\n+            lock.lock();\n+        } catch (...) {\n+            --nThreadsServicingQueue;\n+            throw;\n+        }\n```\n\nIn case `f` throws the statement `--nThreadsServicingQueue;` will run while not protected by the lock. This is a race condition and UB.\n",
